0.1 - 0.6:
* Alpha stage, any code in any order

0.7:
* Initial private beta
* Full security audit
* Open to developer testing only

0.8:
* Second beta to improve upon any feedback gained from 0.7 testing stage
* General polishing
* Open to the public for testing
     
0.9:
* Final beta
* More of everything

1.0_rcX:
* Release candidate stage
* More vigourus testing
* Only bug fixes allowed

1.0:
* Public release!
* Get pissed

Post 1.0 versioning scheme:

1.0.n:
* Bug fix releases

1.n.0:
* Feature releases
